### create poll
POST http://localhost:8080/polls?userId=1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Liker du ananas på pizza",
  "validUntil": "2025-09-20T00:00:00Z"
}

### list polls
GET http://localhost:8080/polls

### Add first option
POST http://localhost:8080/polls/1/options
Content-Type: application/json

{ "caption": "Ja, nam", "presentationOrder": 1 }

### Add second option
POST http://localhost:8080/polls/1/options
Content-Type: application/json

{ "caption": "Nei, æsj", "presentationOrder": 2 }

### 8) List options for the poll
GET http://localhost:8080/polls/1/options

### 9) User 2 votes on the poll
# Suppose VS Code option got id=2; adjust if different
POST http://localhost:8080/polls/1/votes?userId=2&optionId=2

### 10) User 2 changes vote (to 'ja' = optionId=1)
POST http://localhost:8080/polls/1/votes?userId=2&optionId=1

### 11) List votes (global)
GET http://localhost:8080/votes

### 12) Delete the poll
DELETE http://localhost:8080/polls/1

### 13) List votes (should be empty)
GET http://localhost:8080/votes